346772,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩咁都要拎光環"},{"pid":"3b8292fbfec641551e62f4be6cb7f9e7e82cf648","tid":1346772,"uid":84408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:15:16.000Z","msg":"成班同工去緊"},{"pid":"f8010f7cd859fa6e1354e4c3b97346dc5d8def66","tid":1346772,"uid":13176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"轉載以下消息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itzOr1w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitzOr1w.png&h=964b47bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;同工集體報案 將繼續進行&gt;<br />\n<br />\n今日各團體都收到不同消息，很多同工都很擔心行動的安全。臻辦已聯絡元朗警民關係科，對方表示會派警察到現場。我們亦已聯絡First aid team到現場支援！<br />\n<br />\n行動亦已通知記者採訪！<br />\n<br />\n集合時間： 15:30 <br />\n集合地點：朗屏西鐵站月台 （在月台先集合）<br />\n<br />\n行動有一定風險，請出席的參與者作好心理準備！<br />\n<br />\n縱然消息滿天飛，但香港人不可活於恐懼之中，請大家互相照應，保持機警，臨場應變。<br />\n<br />\n還有，我們一齊去，一齊走，不要走散！<br />\n<br />\n發起：<br />\n社工總工會<br />\n社工復興運動<br />\n邵家臻立法會議員辦事處<br />\n張超雄立法會議員辦事處緊急呼籲"},{"pid":"3dabbfa0665968535b8393f7fc71aa0864f46932","tid":1346772,"uid":58292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdff3470ddcbdbab2531b036a1c66861c4d6f8c4","tid":1346772,"uid":276500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:49:47.000Z","msg":"抗爭路上社工們都多次幫手<br />\n拖延左不少時間<br />\n等我地有更多撤退時間<br />\n<br />\n有多方面消息指出<br />\n元朗班仆街今日會出去攪班社工<br />\n<br />\n一齊出！保護社工！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xebQERK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxebQERK.png&h=cf50f324&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:16:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27fbc9c295ab28d04cb32e2f64e19869b1f0abde","tid":1346772,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid